item.description:
You can add some links in your footer.
Zzo footer links: Footer links look and feel You just need to add some params in params.toml file. You can add as many as you want.
1 2 3 4 5 6 7 ... [[footerLinks]] name = &#34;myLink1&#34; link = &#34;https://google.com&#34; [[footerLinks]] name = &#34;myLink2&#34; link = &#34;https://yahoo.com&#34;
